== Charts ==
{{Wikipedia books|The 20/20 Experience}}

Upon the release of ''The 20/20 Experience'', due to digital downloads "Strawberry Bubblegum" charted at number 34 on the [[UK R&B Chart|UK R&B Singles Chart]].<ref name="UKR&BDebut"/> For the week dated March 17, 2013, the song debuted on the South Korea [[Gaon Chart|Gaon International Chart]] at number 22 with sales of 7,089 digital copies.<ref name="South Korea Debut"/>

